data.text: @mnewmanphotos Yes we all did thanks. He loves photography and his drone but don't get out much these days
@mnewmanphotos Went up with my son a few weeks ago and loved it. He met some of his Swedish friends that were over too.
@mnewmanphotos My daughter is a makeup artist and hair stylist doing loads of London shoots, they use Battersea Park a lot👍 Have a good day!

@mnewmanphotos Olympic Park is free & has nice shapes & textures.

The rooftop garden at Crossrail Place in Canary Wharf is quiet on a weekend. Good for Macro pics of plants.

Cannon St for modern glass buildings / architecture shots.

Southbank for water shots & ppl watching.
